; Dev-only greybox for the task-03 manual playtest (F6). Not wired into GameManager —
; mission flow is task 11. Walk/sprint (stamina), crouch/prone, look, and lean Q/E to
; peek the guard around the corner without leaving cover. Positions are tunable.

